          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The total absolute error in the measured",
                "cross section for the best case."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "DATA-ERR2",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The total absolute error in the measured",
                "cross section for the worst case.",
                "The uncertainties include:",
                "1. The nonuniformity in the foil thickness may",
                "introduce a 1 to 2% error.",
                "2. Variations in the incident alpha-particle flux may",
                "introduce an overall error of 6%.",
                "3. The statistical error in the counting of the",
                "standard gamma-source used for the efficiency",
                "calclation was estimated to be around 3%,",
                "4.  The dead time uncertainty introduced the error in",
                "the determination of the photopeak areas within the",
                "limits of 1 to 4%.",
                "5. The errors in the absolute abundance of the",
                "characteristic gamma-rays vary between 1 to 8%.",
                "Straggling effects and the decrease in beam intensity",
                "along stack material were neglected.",
                "The above-mentioned errors do not include the",
                "uncertainty of the decay data."
              ]
            },
